"""
        Test that the inequality operator returns True when comparing two
        KeyWrappingSpecification structs with different attribute names.
        """
a = objects.KeyWrappingSpecification(attribute_names=[
    'Cryptographic Algorithm', 'Cryptographic Length'])
b = objects.KeyWrappingSpecification(attribute_names=[
    'Cryptographic Usage Mask'])
self.assertTrue(a != b)
self.assertTrue(b != a)
